  "type": "Exercise",
  "number": "57",
  "title": "",
  "body": " In 2018, the public debt of the United States was over $20,620,000,000,000.  Express this number in scientific notation.  If the population of the United States in 2018 was 327,112,000, what was the per capita debt (the debt per person) in 2018?     $63,036.51  "
